          <li><strong>Pricing snapshot</strong> — Verified from the official pricing page on the review date. Prices may have changed since then.</li>
          <li><strong>Editable assumption</strong> — Default values in the calculator are illustrative planning estimates, not provider guarantees.</li>
          <li><strong>Derived calculation</strong> — Results computed from the formulas above. Not audited by any provider.</li>
          <li><strong>Provider-specific policy</strong> — Billing behavior that varies by provider, model and account tier.</li>
        </ul>

